[38.495539, "o", "PRD written to `docs/helix/01-frame/prd.md` (~35 lines). Key points:\r\n\r\n- **F-1/F-2**: `GET /health` → HTTP 200 JSON `{\"status\":\"ok\",\"uptime\":<seconds>}`\r\n- **F-3**: all other routes → 404\r\n- Constraints locked to `Bun.serve()`, `bun:test`, Biome per concerns.md\r\n\r\nTracker issue created: **`hello-bun-895585d8`** — \"Implement /health endpoint per PRD\"  \r\n(`--spec-id` isn't a supported flag; the spec reference was folded into `--description` instead.)\r\n\r\n"]
