[137.229703, "o", "What you just saw:\r\n  1. Concerns declared: typescript-bun (Bun, Biome, bun:test)\r\n  2. Agent reads concerns and uses the correct tools\r\n  3. Deliberate drift introduced (vitest import)\r\n  4. Review catches the drift via concern-aware review\r\n\r\n"]
[137.229743, "o", "Concerns prevent the technology drift that happens when\r\nagents (or developers) reach for familiar tools instead\r\nof the project's declared stack.\r\n\r\n"]
